CONTEXT / WHY THESE ARE CANDIDATES
  - The only filesystems in use are ext4 (root) and vfat (EFI). Tools for other
    filesystems (btrfs, xfs, f2fs, jfs, udf) are dead weight here.
  - This is a single-boot, bare-metal, Intel-iGPU machine, so multi-boot,
    VM-guest, and discrete-GPU driver packages are unnecessary.
  - Good news: the live-ISO installer packages you suspected are NOT installed
    (see "ALREADY CLEAN" section) — there is nothing to remove there.

